description:
Batten down the laughter hatches for a barn-storming night of jokes, banter and hilarious micky-taking from Britain's most outrageous comedian, bar none!

You'll explode with laughter as Chubby rips into his live audience with a non-stop battering ram of laugh-out-loud comedy. From motorway pile-ups to marriage counsellors, cancer-causing sausages to asylum seekers' swimming skills, and from disabled parking to why Chubby really is too fat to be gay - this show is grab-your-guts funny!
